    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban pavement parking that blocks pavement users from passing",
        "additional_details": "We believe it\u2019d make it safe and relieving for people who do not want to risk getting hit by a car because the provided pedestrian access has been taken up by a motor vehicle. There are mums, dads and disabled people that rely on the pavement being free to get from A to B safely.",
        "background": "There should be a ban on car, van, and lorry users parking on the pavement in a way that stops pedestrians and other pavement users going past.  We believe it\u2019s a danger to all who may be forced to go around a car or a van and risk getting hit by a vehicle.",
